{
  "stem": "151.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You're not going to find mother and then you're not going to find me either, so please don't go anywhere.' And we were taken into an underground dressing room.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here, surrounded by Nazi soldiers and vicious dogs that were growling and barking at us, we were told we should get undressed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We're going to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were waiting for the soldiers to leave so we can get undressed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And of course nobody moved, so one of the soldiers walked over to one of these women and hit her and said, 'Take it off.' And we realized that they are not leaving.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we started to get undressed, and again we were given orders to be very careful how we fold our belongings, remember exactly where you're leaving your clothing because when you come out of the shower, you will have to hurry up and dress and be assigned to your work.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And still we were naive and stupid enough to believe that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I told my sister to make sure that she puts her stuff next to mine so we don't get separated when we-- when we come out of the shower.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Needless to say that the minute we walked into the shower room, the doors were slammed behind us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Our belongings were picked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came out naked on the other side of the shower room and stood there wet, naked from mid afternoon until about midnight.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember my sister and I hugging each other for a little body warmth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were freezing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then at midnight they took us into this barrack where they shaved our heads, our bodies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sprayed us with DDT, with pesticide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we walked through a door where two prisoners greeted us.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
